    {
      "id": "14c27683-e659-453f-9ce6-ed3ac83299a6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Analytics framework uses a neural network to make predictions after the first, second and third quarters of the course, achiving 88.71% accuracy, 94% F1 Score and 73% AUC.",
